cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper deals with optimization of distributed learning systems, which is a topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses communication compression and decentralization, which are topics in distributed computing, making cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) likely categories as well. The paper also proposes algorithms and analyzes their convergence rates, which falls under the category of control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with neural networks, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category as well.
